TopicTitle: N11 - Soviet Style Rocket With Munar Spacecraft

Articles.Content:
I'm not good at intros, so lets get to the rocket.

This is the N11, which is essentially a N1 without the Block A. It comes with a Spacecraft and TMI stage. You can modify the payload to anything up to about 20 tons.
